https://oorischubert.com.desc: Homepage of Oori Schubert, featuring a projects list and links to About, Projects, Contact, and Resume pages. Main point of entry for Oori's personal and professional showcase.

https://oorischubert.com/about.html.desc: About page for Oori Schubert. Introduces Oori: 'Hey I'm Oori, I build things.' Includes a placeholder indicating more content will be added in the future, and an animated picture of Oori.

https://oorischubert.com/contact.html.desc: Contact page for Oori Schubert. Provides quick access to Oori's LinkedIn, GitHub, X (Twitter), email, and WhatsApp.

https://oorischubert.com/documents/Ooris.desc: PDF document of Oori Schubert's Resume. Open for more details about Oori's professional background.

https://oorischubert.com/projectPages/tu.desc: TurtleBot project page for Oori Schubert. Contains images, links to the project's GitHub repository and 3D models, and an embedded 3D viewer. Focused on robotics hardware/software.

https://oorischubert.com/projectPages/ca.desc: CapTouch project page. Features an image of the CapTouch device, but does not provide further descriptive details.
